programmes.show_description: Programmes Start at 07:00.
Oona cannot sleep because she is excited about her first dawn chorus.
Oona heads out to sea to play with a whale, and Baba decides to make his own way home.
Happy and his friends feel very excited waiting for caterpillars to turn into butterflies.
Bingo: When Bluey has a playdate at Chloe's, Bingo must learn how to play by herself.
Stuck in the Traffic with You: Oswaldo gets stuck in traffic when going on a family trip and finds his friends are too.
Bad Hair Day: When Mitchell locks himself in the school bathroom, Oswaldo tries to negotiate him out.
Daniel receives a new doll from Grandpere. When Katerina and O insist that Daniel pretends to be Tigey the Adventure Tiger, Daniel reminds them that you can be more than one thing.
Calcium & Aluminium learn to be themselves and embrace their quirkiness as they take part in the prestigious Atom Town Dance Off.
Dee encourages a friend to say 't', and we go on an adventure around the sound. We meet a turtle, shake our tails and see a tiger in a tall tent!
When Grandmaster Glitch takes the quadriga from the Brandenburg Gate, the Go Jetters must stop him before he reaches Grim HQ.
Ted wants more speed, and Bo's rocket gives him a lot more than he expected!
Miss BimBamBoom: Tonight is circus night in Minusville. Nina dreams of doing an acrobatic act, but Fifi, who is afraid of heights, turns it into a clown act.
Out of the Box: Titus is having a bad day and takes refuge in his cereal box. Oli will do everything he can to encourage him to play and tinker again.

programmes.show_name: Lex and Plu Space Taxi Drivers
programmes.show_description: Planet Bounce: Lex and Plu need to deliver a young Frog, Casper Ribbits, home to Planet Castoff. When they arrive, our heroes meet Victor and Toma Ribbits, the Casper's parents.
Saving Pigeon Post: During a game of hide and seek, Doodle gets a funny feeling that Pigeon Post is in trouble. Together with the flamingos, they leave the game in order to rescue Pigeon Post.
Dawn Chorus: An all-musical episode in which Odo, Doodle and all the campers sing and dance their way through a morning where Odo's big quest is to bake muffins for breakfast.
As the sun begins to set and stop their shadow game, Hugo and Sonia learn there are more ways than one to play. (SL)
Sonia finds her chosen garden chores tricky until she learns to ask for help. (SL)
World Elevator Hike: A tiny planet suddenly appears hovering above Marzipan's house. Fuzzy Yellow, Marzipan and Bennu get a ride up to the wee new world and explore it. (SL)

Henry meets a friendly whale and learns all about how they breath underwater.
Farm: Stanley helps Amare with some planting and harvesting, but of course Stanley has some ideas to make it faster and more fun.
Dig: Fifi and Fred discover some old stones while digging.

programmes.show_name: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
programmes.show_description: The Sights of Sodor: Sir Topham Hatt places a plaque at the top of Lookout Mountain so that tourists can take in all of Sodor in just one sight. Thomas takes visitors to really see Sodor.
Ray discovers that it's Duff's birthday and wants to chalk up the best birthday present ever for her, so he'll need a little help from his friends.
Flamingo Frolics: It's a special day at Peek Zoo, when visitors gather to watch the flamingos dance to attract a mate.
The Bird That Wouldn't Sing: Wendy finds a nightingale with a sore wing, so Mr Peek puts it in the aviary where they can keep an eye on it.
Tá Granny, Grandpa, Peppa agus George ag dul ag campáil cois trá. Téann siad ann sa seanghluaisrothar agus carr cliathánach.
Dúisíonn Peppa agus George i bpuball ghluaisrothar Granny agus Grandpa cois farraige. Feiceann Peppa páipéar i mbuidéal le huimhir teileafóin air.
Fionn gifts all his musical instruments to his friends. Oisín and Rúbaí decide to create new hand-made instruments for the music festival for him.
Henny is a very active hippopotamus who plays football and tennis. After a very active day, Henny loves nothing more than a long soak in the bath.
Camille is quite a playful crocodile, who dreams of being a ballerina.
Simon is bored and wishes to go on a holiday. He shows his friends that with a big imagination you can travel anywhere.
Carnivore Club: Reggie and the others decide to bring food together for a shared meal. Huey brings mushrooms, Kenny brings potatoes, Grace brings water plants, and Reggie and Nemi bring clams.
